---
title: Nan’s Creamy Pork Penne with Baby Leaves & Parmesan
description: We have a dilemma, those herby pork look so tasty but we’re also really wanting a creamy pasta. If you feel the same, then the solution is right here - let’s have both in a pork sausage penne! There’s no need for compromise when you can have both!

*We’ve replaced the fusilli in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

